Homework

Create the following script:

1. login
2. click the Add button
3. enter first and last name
4. save the employee code
5. click the Create Login Details checkbox
6. enter the username - it must be unique, so use the code as part of your username
(first + last + employee code)
7. enter the password ('password') and click Save
8. ensure the record was fully saved - by ensuring you reach the Personal Details page for the new employee
9. logout
10. login as the new employee and check that the correct welcome message is displayed (Welcome <first_name>)

The goal of this homework is to practise adding appropriate WebDriverWait where applicable.
So debug, and add wait anywhere you would usually use time.sleep()


